{"tid":163384,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"強烈建議admin增設呢個功能","createTime":"2017-03-20T02:43:28.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-20T23:01:32.000Z","uid":19155,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0527669f0717f7aec2f46e29758ea8fe8f3dfe0a","tid":163384,"uid":19155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T02:43:28.000Z","msg":"用戶說話被quote嘅時候發出reminder提醒<br />\n<br />\n之前都應該有人提出過<br />\n<br />\n個人覺得呢個功能可以增加交流，互動性<br />\n<br />\n有時想問一啲會員問題或者進行下一步嘅討論，但好多時對方就無咗下文，或者因為太多留言根本見唔到自己對話被quote,冇辦法作出回應，大大減低咗互動性<br />\n<br />\n其他好壞處有待提出<br />\n歡迎討論<br />\n<br />\n如果admin對呢個提議有任何意見，請作出回覆<br />\n如果之前已經有結論，我自膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07531d29c7d3d6f9e4bcb31d5ff93d3b6fc68831","tid":163384,"uid":19155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T03:00:06.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9880722b048324abcde9e107e2bd415872bf826d","tid":163384,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T03:36:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"743cf2053d4074eec72fcff261a45019e6ce57c8","tid":163384,"uid":7555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T03:38:32.000Z","msg":"俾人quote<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 都幾嘈"},{"pid":"f1ec3e9fcc3e43ecde2057d89c40d914d4585c75","tid":163384,"uid":19155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T04:34:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>俾人quote<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 都幾嘈</blockquote><br /